<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Rothenburg ob der Tauber</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt die gewünschte Entsendung von Botschaftern nach Windsheim und bittet bei Verhinderung um Nachricht.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_284" id="141v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_284_r1l1"><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_284_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / daʒ vvir ew vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l4"> <expan>erbe<ex>r</ex></expan> botſchaft <expan>leẏh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd dıe 
<del rend="strikethrough">auf </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_284_r1l3">gen wındſheim </ab></add> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan> auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l5">den <expan>nehſtkünftıge<ex>n</ex></expan> Dornſtag cʒu naht do cʒeſein <expan>ſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l6">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan></del> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / daſſelb wir alſo durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l7">tun wöllen vnd <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntſchaft / ob das wer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l8">daʒ icht darein viel alſo daʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freunde auf <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l11">niht dahin <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>würde<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vns das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_284_r1l9">vor </ab></add> <expan>cʒuvviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l12">wöllet / daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht vmb ſüſt reẏten / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r1l13"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>anis</ex></expan> <expan>Bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_284" id="141v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, daz wir ew unser
                                <expan>erbe<ex>r</ex></expan> botschaft
                            <expan>leyh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und die <add>gen Windsheim</add> czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freunde<ex>n</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                            <expan>nehstkünftige<ex>n</ex></expan> dornstag</q>25.06.1411</note></app> czu naht do cze sein
                                <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>, dasselb wir also durch
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun
                        wöllen. Und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntschaft, ob das wer, daz icht darein viel,
                        also daz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freunde auf <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> tag niht dahin
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>würde<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz ir uns das <add>vor</add>
<expan>czu wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> tun wöllet, daz die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht umb süst reyten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>anis</ex></expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
